# AI Quiz Generator

An AI-powered quiz generator built with Python and Streamlit.

## Created by
Iqra & Imsal

## Description
Enter any topic and this app will instantly generate a 5-question multiple choice quiz using Groq AI.

## Technologies Used
- Python 3.11
- Streamlit
- Groq AI API (LLaMA 3.3 model)

## How to Use
1. Open the app link
2. Enter any topic (e.g. Solar System, Pakistan History)
3. Click Generate Quiz
4. Answer the questions
5. See your final score

## Live App
[Cick here to open my app](https://iqrashafiq315-web-ai-quiz-generator-iqra-imsal-quiz-app-11ddtb.streamlit.app/)
